\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T07:59:17.000Z","msg":"掃描曱尺印記<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76afc941338985ea80bbd06ee0f00a1d89e83c30","tid":2403591,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T13:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de55f1e0462bf23f0816831a74066f102dee80ec","tid":2403591,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T14:11:37.000Z","msg":"額頭同手受印<br />\n其實都幾明顯係探熱<br />\n啟示錄真係好鯪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4b7b83deca448f20c96750470814b7940159eb","tid":2403591,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:41:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32b702f35c3471b15f18f83535833ab7d44aa82","tid":2403591,"uid":363330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:43:01.000Z","msg":"大淫婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"c363753c69984c5a68c1c7e5507f6c62ae84c4d7","tid":2403591,"uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T07:30:40.000Z","msg":"基督教信仰分享頻道<br />\n<br />\nTelegram: @gospelsharing"}}